text: Interstate 105 (I-105) is the name of three Interstate Highways in the United States that are spurs of the Interstate 5: * Interstate 105 (California), a spur of Interstate 5 in Los Angeles County, California * Interstate 105 (California 1964-1968), a former part of U.S. Route 101 in Downtown Los Angeles, California * Interstate 105 (Oregon), a spur of Interstate 5 in Eugene, Oregon Category:Interstate Highways
title: Interstate 105
